{
 "name": "RPlog_Piper_Speaks_with_Kuxli",
 "title": "Piper Speaks with Kuxli",
 "summary": "In the Government District of Capital City on Etti IV, the CSA VicePrex Piper seeks out the young Horansi cub Kuxli, sitting brooding at a fountain, to finish a conversation cut short the night before. Coldly professional, Piper makes no apology for having had her guards shoot Kuxli, insisting she acted solely in the best interests of the Authority and that he should trust her over his friends in Caspar and the New Republic. The bitter, sarcastic Kuxli rejects her reasoning, declaring they have nothing more to discuss before walking off into CSA headquarters. Piper departs unmoved, later recording a terse transmission to Sean Dillon noting her early return to Etti IV.",
